Package: giphyR
Type: Package
Title: Programmatic wrapper for the giphy API (https://github.com/Giphy/GiphyAPI)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Simon Goring
Maintainer: Simon Goring <simon.j.goring@gmail.com>
Description: The package downloads information about GIF images from Giphy
    (http://giphy.com) and plots them using the magick package for R.  Plotting
    requires the installation of ImageMagick (https://www.imagemagick.org/script/download.php).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
Imports:
    magick,
    jsonlite,
    httr,
    dplyr
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
